Here, you will be given several quiz questions. If
you answer incorrectly, there will be a penalty of
minus \c[0]count, but whether you answer correctly
or incorrectly, you can proceed \c[0]either way.

Furthermore, there will be a reward when you
answer all the questions correctly.

and 12,000 aircraft were deployed.

\n<Monitor>\C[24]On what year, month, and day did the
operation led by General Eisenhower of the Anglo-
American Allied Forces, which landed in a certain
region of northern France, take place? (Example:

\n<Monitor>\C[24]The ability to completely grasp and analyze
all mechanical and physical states that are acting
at a certain point in time enables one to
definitively know the entire motion of the
universe, including the future.

mathematician that refers to the concept of
\C[24]superhuman intelligence?
